### Sweven Events API Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = https://api.swevenevents.com/v1
@userToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
@organizerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ========================================
### EVENTS API
### ========================================

### 1. Get All Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Events with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?city=Los%20Angeles&category=Music&featured=true&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Search Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/search?q=festival&city=Miami
Content-Type: application/json

### ========================================
### BOOKINGS API
### ========================================

### 5. Create Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "eventId": "evt_1a2b3c4d5e",
  "ticketTierId": "tier_abc123",
  "quantity": 2,
  "attendee": {
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "phone": "+1-555-0199"
  },
  "addOns": ["addon_1", "addon_2"],
  "promoCode": "EARLYBIRD",
  "paymentMethod": {
    "type": "card",
    "token": "tok_visa_4242424242424242"
  }
}

### 6. Get User Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?status=confirmed&page=1&limit=20
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 7. Get Booking Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/bkg_9z8y7x6w5v
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 8. Cancel Booking
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bookings/bkg_9z8y7x6w5v
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 9. Download Ticket PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/bkg_9z8y7x6w5v/tickets/download
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ========================================
### PROMO CODES API
### ========================================

### 10. Validate Promo Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/promo-codes/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "EARLYBIRD",
  "eventId": "evt_1a2b3c4d5e",
  "ticketTierId": "tier_abc123",
  "quantity": 2
}

### ========================================
### ORGANIZER API
### ========================================

### 11. Create Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "title": "Summer Music Festival 2026",
  "subtitle": "The hottest acts of summer",
  "description": "Join us for an unforgettable weekend of music, food, and fun under the stars.",
  "category": "Music",
  "date": "2026-07-15T17:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-07-17T23:00:00Z",
  "venue": {
    "name": "Beachside Arena",
    "address": "123 Ocean Drive",
    "city": "Miami",
    "state": "FL",
    "zipCode": "33139",
    "coordinates": {
      "lat": 25.7617,
      "lng": -80.1918
    }
  },
  "ticketTiers": [
    {
      "name": "General Admission",
      "price": 99.00,
      "description": "Standard entry with access to all stages",
      "totalSeats": 5000,
      "features": ["All stages access", "Festival grounds", "Food court"]
    },
    {
      "name": "VIP Pass",
      "price": 299.00,
      "description": "Premium experience with exclusive perks",
      "totalSeats": 500,
      "features": ["VIP lounge", "Premium viewing areas", "Complimentary drinks", "Fast-track entry"]
    }
  ],
  "tags": ["Music", "Festival", "Summer"],
  "isFeatured": false,
  "status": "draft"
}

### 12. Update Event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "title": "Updated Event Title",
  "status": "published"
}

### 13. Get Organizer Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events?status=published&page=1&limit=20
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 14. Get Event Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/analytics?period=30d
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 15. Get Real-Time Event Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/stats/realtime
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 16. Export Event Attendees
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/attendees/export?format=csv
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 17. Create Promo Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/promo-codes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "code": "SUMMER25",
  "discountType": "percentage",
  "discountValue": 25,
  "maxUses": 100,
  "validFrom": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "validUntil": "2026-06-15T23:59:59Z",
  "applicableTiers": ["tier_abc123", "tier_def456"],
  "minimumPurchase": 1
}

### 18. Get Promo Codes
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/promo-codes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 19. Deactivate Promo Code
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/organizer/promo-codes/promo_xyz123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### ========================================
### NOTIFICATIONS API
### ========================================

### 20. Send Event Reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "type": "reminder",
  "channel": ["email", "sms"],
  "template": "event_reminder_24h",
  "scheduledFor": "2026-03-14T18:00:00Z",
  "recipientFilter": {
    "bookingStatus": "confirmed"
  }
}

### 21. Send Event Update
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizer/events/evt_1a2b3c4d5e/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "type": "update",
  "channel": ["email"],
  "template": "event_update",
  "subject": "Important Update: Event Time Changed",
  "message": "Due to weather conditions, the event start time has been moved to 7 PM.",
  "recipientFilter": {
    "bookingStatus": "confirmed"
  }
}

### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATION API
### ========================================

### 22. User Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "phone": "+1-555-0199"
}

### 23. User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 24. Organizer Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/organizer/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "organizer@swevenevents.com",
  "password": "secureOrgPassword123"
}

### 25. Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "ref_tok_xyz789..."
}

### 26. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 27. Reset Password Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset-request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### 28. Reset Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "reset_token_abc123",
  "newPassword": "newSecurePassword123"
}

### ========================================
### TICKET SCANNING API
### ========================================

### 29. Validate Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "ticketNumber": "SWE-001-2026-001",
  "eventId": "evt_1a2b3c4d5e"
}

### 30. Check-in Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "ticketId": "tkt_001",
  "eventId": "evt_1a2b3c4d5e",
  "checkinTime": "2026-03-15T18:15:00Z",
  "location": "Main Entrance"
}

### ========================================
### PAYMENT API
### ========================================

### 31. Create Payment Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/intent
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": 235.62,
  "currency": "USD",
  "bookingId": "bkg_9z8y7x6w5v"
}

### 32. Process Refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/refund
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "bookingId": "bkg_9z8y7x6w5v",
  "amount": 235.62,
  "reason": "event_cancelled"
}

### ========================================
### ANALYTICS & REPORTING
### ========================================

### 33. Get Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/dashboard/summary
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 34. Get Revenue Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/reports/revenue?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 35. Get Booking Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/analytics/booking-trends?eventId=evt_1a2b3c4d5e&period=30d
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### ========================================
### WEBHOOKS
### ========================================

### 36. List Webhooks
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizer/webhooks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 37. Create Webhook
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizer/webhooks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "url": "https://your-domain.com/webhooks/sweven-events",
  "events": [
    "booking.created",
    "booking.confirmed",
    "booking.cancelled",
    "payment.completed"
  ],
  "secret": "whsec_your_webhook_secret"
}

### 38. Test Webhook
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizer/webhooks/wh_abc123/test
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

{
  "eventType": "booking.created"
}
